76
00:03:11,121 --> 00:03:12,443
and weight is 80 kg.

77
00:03:12,443 --> 00:03:16,762
So my BMR is 1828 calories per day.

78
00:03:16,762 --> 00:03:20,347
So I will burn this many calories every day
