200
00:09:06,177 --> 00:09:11,103
Proteins, carbohydrates, fats, 
vitamins, minerals, and water.

201
00:09:11,103 --> 00:09:13,087
So when you are on a healthy weight loss diet,

202
00:09:13,087 --> 00:09:17,026
you will definitely need proteins, vitamins,
minerals, and water.

203
00:09:17,026 --> 00:09:20,131
Now the question is about 
